quran[13]{c,v,t}:
  36,28,"Wama anzalna AAalaqawmihi min baAAdihi min jundin mina assama-i wamakunna munzileen"
  36,29,"In kanat illa sayhatanwahidatan fa-itha hum khamidoon"
  36,30,"Ya hasratan AAalaalAAibadi ma ya/teehim min rasoolin illa kanoobihi yastahzi-oon"
  36,31,"Alam yaraw kam ahlakna qablahum minaalqurooni annahum ilayhim la yarjiAAoon"
  36,32,"Wa-in kullun lamma jameeAAun ladaynamuhdaroon"
  36,33,"Waayatun lahumu al-ardualmaytatu ahyaynaha waakhrajna minhahabban faminhu ya/kuloon"
  36,34,"WajaAAalna feeha jannatinmin nakheelin waaAAnabin wafajjarna feehamina alAAuyoon"
  36,35,"Liya/kuloo min thamarihi wamaAAamilat-hu aydeehim afala yashkuroon"
  36,36,"Subhana allathee khalaqaal-azwaja kullaha mimma tunbitu al-arduwamin anfusihim wamimma la yaAAlamoon"
  36,37,"Waayatun lahumu allaylu naslakhuminhu annahara fa-itha hum muthlimoon"
  36,38,"Washshamsu tajree limustaqarrin lahathalika taqdeeru alAAazeezi alAAaleem"
  36,39,"Walqamara qaddarnahu manazilahatta AAada kalAAurjooni alqadeem"
  36,40,"La ashshamsu yanbaghee lahaan tudrika alqamara wala allaylu sabiqu annahariwakullun fee falakin yasbahoon"
